*** configure alt-tab to cycle through all workspaces

configure alt-tab to cycle through all workspaces
Change:
 
 <keybind key="A-Tab">
 <action name="NextWindow"/>
 </keybind>
 to:
 
 <keybind key="A-Tab">
 <action name="NextWindow"/>
 <allDesktops>yes</allDesktops>
 </keybind>
 in ~/.config/openbox/rc.xml

*** hebrew

Get hebrew indicator and hebrew switch

