 go down nicklist /D
 register zeltak nick /nic

****** my binds

` is bound to the /go command
 ctrl+down: input history global next
 ctrl+up: input history global prev
 key alt-x to toggle nicklist bar: /key bind meta-x /bar toggle
nicklist

