**** tabs

***** MOVING BETWEEN TABS

If you have a couple of tabs open you can switch btwn them with gt and
gT, but if you have 5 or six tabs open:
 b + # of tab <Enter>
 The tabs numbers run from 1 starting from left to right.
 Example:
 So, if you want to move to tab #5:
 b + 5 <Enter>

