sudo dhclient <interface>
#+END_EXAMPLE
 
Example:

#+BEGIN_SRC sh
sudo dhclient eth0
#+END_SRC
 
and this will look for a dhcp server and tell you the ip address it is
given and lets you know when it will expire.
 
