    emacs and i3 updates

commit d4e7b0d0afb8d57a5954a310d59a20c1f1d7c234
Author: zeltak <zeltak@gmail.com>
Date:   Tue Apr 9 17:39:51 2013 -0400

    added emacs

commit 30d43652a1f225d9379e8d06c3f9fdbec580b242
