can have anything ranging from a /dev/dvd, /dev/dvdrw, /dev/dvd1
/dev/dvdrw1
 setup the correct path in Mythdvd settingsEject and close tray from
command line
 eject /dev/cdrom1
 to close tray:
 eject -t /dev/cdrom1

